{"tid":2281832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要鬧嘅嘢鬧完，依家究竟點走落去？","createTime":"2020-11-11T11:34:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T11:57:42.000Z","uid":33939,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4fc6cd8663b03a03306b5891303eac008eb0ff","tid":2281832,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:34:29.000Z","msg":"老蕭就話總辭之後搞民間議政，當然佢講果時係叫泛民唔好被委任，而去搞哩啲嘢。依家佢哋先辭究竟仲有冇人信報(無論唔支持/唔支持佢哋被委任)，而且亦有冇膽搞呢？<br />\n<br />\n雖然老蕭話只係講下民生嘢，唔好講政治嘢，但實有人忍唔住/又或者有鬼。<br />\n就算你真係咁乖只講民生嘢，對中共嚟講都係篤口篤鼻，隨時出鄉黑，甚至直接屈你犯國安法拉人封艇。"},{"pid":"e3df90b234050e8e40caa0dafc9ae391ff07535d","tid":2281832,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"國際線<br />\n撐侵侵<br />\n老實搵錢<br />\n移民"},{"pid":"d8b105d801d156aa9b02cad918e193e0f782e1c7","tid":2281832,"uid":126142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:37:42.000Z","msg":"做猶太人"},{"pid":"4efdda7d14168b9d3f5b52b41d60fe937455a2d8","tid":2281832,"uid":69895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"英國建立香港流亡政府"},{"pid":"9891731477d74732a29743b9e118d89fc4ab7de8","tid":2281832,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"去建制派入面鬥紅<br />\n批鬥做唔到野既建制派<br />\n何巳完係先鋒 可先附和佢"},{"pid":"c1081b8a9bb0a75a9a7ee6bd25116f8727dc3902","tid":2281832,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3df90b234050e8e40caa0dafc9ae391ff07535d","tid":2281832,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"國際線<br />\n撐侵侵<br />\n老實搵錢<br />\n移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"國際線算係最後一絲光或海海市晨樓，如果美國最尾同中國和解，真係得移民。"},{"pid":"b64e850c6e4776720365040a2ebe7d547a514254","tid":2281832,"uid":114946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9891731477d74732a29743b9e118d89fc4ab7de8","tid":2281832,"uid":268591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T1